Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.03,0:00:19.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.03,0:00:20.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,还是起来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.84,0:02:04.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,「3月13日  3%的希望」
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.87,0:02:07.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊～
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.51,0:02:09.09,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我真是没用啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.46,0:02:12.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,干吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.82,0:02:13.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,假装外出
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.82,0:02:13.96,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,（注：原文“居留守番”，此“居留守”即假装外出不在家之意，\N躲避债务等的必杀技）
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.56,0:02:28.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,早安～
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.08,0:02:32.02,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,早上好  进来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.21,0:02:34.93,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哦  由乃你干过些什么吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.32,0:02:37.93,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,忽然想画点什么了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.24,0:02:38.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.17,0:02:40.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,再不久就是春天了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.36,0:02:44.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我们进山吹高中的时候也正是春天
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.88,0:02:48.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我想看看自己的画功到底长进到什么地步了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.66,0:02:49.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哦～
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.97,0:02:50.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.17,0:02:53.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,完全不能下笔
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.69,0:02:54.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,今天也是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.63,0:02:56.14,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,难得的休息日
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.31,0:02:58.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,本想从早上开始集中精神画的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.88,0:03:00.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,却刚刚才睡醒过来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.18,0:03:03.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我也是两分钟之前起来的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.91,0:03:05.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真是失望啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.93,0:03:08.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,实际上我都还没决定要画什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.90,0:03:10.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,感觉有点懒散呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.24,0:03:13.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是不是因为没有截止日期呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.64,0:03:14.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,也许是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.88,0:03:16.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我也来画些什么吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.73,0:03:17.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,借我桌子一用
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.08,0:03:20.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那么…画猫吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.48,0:03:23.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,有爪子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.74,0:03:25.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这家伙可是非常强的哟
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.82,0:03:28.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这样的话就能很畅快地画下去了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.52,0:03:32.27,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哦～
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.61,0:03:33.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真可爱呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.10,0:03:35.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.53,0:03:36.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,接下来呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.61,0:03:38.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯　花怎么样？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.93,0:03:40.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,花瓣…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.74,0:03:41.22,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,喜欢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.36,0:03:41.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不喜欢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.10,0:03:42.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,喜欢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.72,0:03:43.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不喜欢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.81,0:03:44.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,喜欢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.64,0:03:45.27,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不喜欢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.55,0:03:45.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,喜欢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.20,0:03:46.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不喜欢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.74,0:03:46.90,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,（扯花瓣占卜这个算是个人就知道的玩意了吧）
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.29,0:03:48.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,完成了！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.34,0:03:49.09,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.78,0:03:51.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,再不久就是春天了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.76,0:03:52.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你这是猫？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.35,0:03:54.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真的好逼真
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.92,0:03:55.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,接下来画米饭
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.08,0:03:56.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.73,0:03:58.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是这个样子的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.65,0:04:02.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  还缺少点色彩
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.89,0:04:11.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  是沙英学姐
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.11,0:04:14.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,现在有空的话到我房间来一下
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.63,0:04:19.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不过我希望你从院子那边的窗子进来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.01,0:04:20.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.00,0:04:24.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,振翅高飞吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.40,0:04:25.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊～  小宫
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.78,0:04:28.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,十点零
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.91,0:04:30.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哪…哪里是了…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.61,0:04:31.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.41,0:04:33.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,天空的颜色好漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.31,0:04:37.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,由乃的粉色内裤也不错
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.45,0:04:37.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.31,0:04:46.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好疼…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.93,0:04:47.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,由乃你尽力了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.72,0:04:50.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才好象有什么声音…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.74,0:04:52.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,呀嗬  我们跳下来了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.17,0:04:55.02,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真的是跳下来的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.30,0:04:57.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,诶？真从上面跳下来的？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.15,0:05:00.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,从后院绕过来就好了的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.12,0:05:02.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我们倒是没事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.85,0:05:04.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不过为什么要从院子这边进来呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.02,0:05:08.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,眼下我是在假装外出
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.59,0:05:11.93,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,所以被人看见有人进出就不妙了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.35,0:05:12.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.04,0:05:14.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么怎么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.76,0:05:15.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是负债未还？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.73,0:05:16.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,别以为我是你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.68,0:05:22.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小说的截稿日期就在眼前了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.36,0:05:24.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我在躲着那帮编辑呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.89,0:05:26.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,写小说是工作吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.12,0:05:28.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,太帅了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.56,0:05:30.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,一点也不帅啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.66,0:05:32.94,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,过了截稿日期还是一个字没写
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.38,0:05:34.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.17,0:05:35.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.19,0:05:39.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,做好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.32,0:05:41.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,帮助沙英老师彻底摆脱烦恼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.03,0:05:44.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,宫子特制故事构思卡片
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.33,0:05:47.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我还以为你要干什么呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.31,0:05:53.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,谁…在哪里…把什么…怎么样…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.31,0:05:53.11,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,（小学作文的所谓四要素之类的东西吧…）
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.32,0:05:54.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,随机抽卡片的话
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.07,0:05:58.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,瞬间故事的构思就出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.54,0:05:59.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,开始了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.04,0:06:00.93,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,和尚…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.37,0:06:02.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,在草原上…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.85,0:06:03.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,把青花鱼…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.30,0:06:05.09,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,给蒸了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.70,0:06:07.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,和尚在草原上把青花鱼给蒸了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.53,0:06:10.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你给我去写
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.21,0:06:12.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,在草原上…青花鱼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.03,0:06:16.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我说  我可是很重视亲身体会的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.23,0:06:22.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我觉得自己没有经历过的事情就不能写得很真实
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.17,0:06:24.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,沙英学姐真了不起
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.98,0:06:27.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是对这个比较看重…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.73,0:06:30.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那不就不能写恋爱故事了么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.60,0:06:33.16,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,沙英学姐可是和这种事情绝缘的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.19,0:06:35.56,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真没礼貌
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.99,0:06:37.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,说的是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.37,0:06:40.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,沙英学姐恋爱经验似乎很丰富的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.15,0:06:44.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那个嘛…当然…初中的时候啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.59,0:06:46.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,男朋友都有八个之多…太够戗…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.72,0:06:49.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,还采取预选制度什么的…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.74,0:06:54.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,呃  说来是为什么叫我们来？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.64,0:06:57.02,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,（Berry店）
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.74,0:06:56.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,欢迎光临
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.37,0:06:57.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.40,0:07:00.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我去拿营养饮料
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.70,0:07:02.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,干鱿鱼就拜托由乃你了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.81,0:07:03.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.25,0:07:05.12,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,（副食区  愉快的聚会上  给孩子们做零食）
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.27,0:07:05.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯～
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.12,0:07:07.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,拿哪个好呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.05,0:07:10.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,Berry店的零食种类不少呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.41,0:07:14.00,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,（长生不老之药  清仓）
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.62,0:07:13.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小宫
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.20,0:07:14.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.28,0:07:16.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,看上去好可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.46,0:07:17.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就要这个吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.20,0:07:19.16,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,乌贼君
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.77,0:07:22.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我认为那不是敬称
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.74,0:07:26.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,多谢惠顾
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.31,0:07:29.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,一共九百四十五日圆
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.57,0:07:32.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,沙英学姐是算好了才给的一千日圆的钞票的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.56,0:07:36.04,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,（最新刊物专区）
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.47,0:07:35.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.85,0:07:43.11,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7}两个有假名出现的书名，左起：\N暖阳庄之谜\N真实的涅它故事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.81,0:07:40.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是橘文哟
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.58,0:07:41.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真的么？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.63,0:07:42.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我刚在屋里看到的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.91,0:07:44.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  这个
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.28,0:07:46.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这个是沙英学姐么？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.28,0:07:49.12,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,（月刊亮晶晶）
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.02,0:07:49.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  在封面上有名字
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.34,0:07:49.63,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,在哪里？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.75,0:07:50.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,在哪里？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.23,0:07:54.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,呃  九十八页
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.65,0:07:56.01,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,由乃  在更前面
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.37,0:07:56.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.72,0:08:02.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,优香并没有去送
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.53,0:08:03.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那或许是因为
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.54,0:08:09.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,她不愿意承认姐姐将要远走这个事实
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.25,0:08:12.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,美香有点坐立不安
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.96,0:08:17.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,想见优香和不想见的感情交织在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.50,0:08:21.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,优香的预定的日子到来了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.69,0:08:24.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,一早美香有点坐立不安
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.67,0:08:26.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,想见优香…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.13,0:08:31.17,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,然后  优香和美香分别了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.37,0:08:35.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊～
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.51,0:08:36.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,等等  先别说
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.12,0:08:39.11,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7}（饭团）
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.12,0:08:39.11,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an3}（书）
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.41,0:08:44.90,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7}（外卖店）
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.41,0:08:44.90,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an3}（拍卖  28%）
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.61,0:08:40.19,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.77,0:08:41.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,寻学姐
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.53,0:08:43.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀呀
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.53,0:08:44.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,去购物的么？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.59,0:08:47.14,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,买了一大堆呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.60,0:08:50.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  要给沙英做晚饭
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.49,0:08:53.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,截稿日期前一直都是如此
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.82,0:08:56.97,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,正是在这么够戗的时候才希望她能吃好些
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.23,0:08:57.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,寻学姐
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.90,0:08:59.19,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我也是临近截稿日期的了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.52,0:09:01.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小宫  这可不行哟
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.36,0:09:03.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,沙英学姐是真的很辛苦的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.11,0:09:04.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,寻学姐
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.40,0:09:08.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,沙英学姐为什么会到山吹高中的美术科来呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.35,0:09:11.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,明明都可以把写小说作为工作了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.30,0:09:15.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  或许和由乃你们说也没关系呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.17,0:09:16.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,沙英啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.29,0:09:21.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,她是希望能为自己的小说画插图
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.65,0:09:26.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,说是只有她自己才能画得和想的一致
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.02,0:09:29.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真厉害  沙英学姐太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.96,0:09:30.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哦～
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.01,0:09:32.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,绝妙的自导自演
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.29,0:09:35.97,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,可你的说法不大对劲…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.74,0:09:37.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我们回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.78,0:09:39.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.05,0:09:41.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,安…安静一点
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.66,0:09:43.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好象现在进展不错
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.05,0:09:45.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我们先走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.90,0:09:46.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好…好…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.54,0:09:48.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,放在这里了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.68,0:09:53.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,放了一晚上的咖喱
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.69,0:09:55.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  真好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.30,0:09:58.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不过觉得过意不去…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.44,0:09:59.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,有什么过意不去的？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.54,0:10:03.14,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,隔壁沙英学姐不是在工作么？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.78,0:10:06.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,而我们却顾着自己在这里吃…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.63,0:10:10.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,沙英一集中精神好象就不想吃东西了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.35,0:10:13.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,说什么忘记肚子饿了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.18,0:10:15.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小说减肥？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.17,0:10:17.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那寻学姐你也写吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.27,0:10:20.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,工作之后还会补回来的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.86,0:10:22.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我觉得这没什么意义
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.91,0:10:25.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那就对身体不好了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.35,0:10:27.01,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.46,0:10:30.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我还是希望她能好好吃饭的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.20,0:10:35.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,虽说我给她也准备过可以边写边吃的东西…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.14,0:10:40.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,饭团啊三明治啊柿饼什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.37,0:10:42.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,说起三明治
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.59,0:10:45.27,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好象是从前一个非常喜欢玩扑克的伯爵
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.86,0:10:50.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,为了能一边玩扑克一边吃而发明的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.60,0:10:52.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,然后
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.44,0:10:57.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,因为这位伯爵的名字而得名「三明治」
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.14,0:10:59.02,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你们知道么？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.42,0:10:59.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.97,0:11:03.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,即便如此沙英学姐也不肯吃么？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.36,0:11:07.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,对她都觉得无可奈何了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.60,0:11:12.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,截稿日前她总是会变得生活不规律
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.73,0:11:15.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,甚至有的时候她都不睡觉哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.81,0:11:19.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,喝所谓的营养饮料吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.76,0:11:21.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这么年轻就开始这样…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.75,0:11:23.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真是为她的将来担忧啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.58,0:11:28.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那么紧张的话就会变得有些神经质的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.60,0:11:30.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你们还没见过吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.54,0:11:32.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.60,0:11:36.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这种情况下即使是送饭去
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.44,0:11:38.09,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,也会尽量不弄出声音来
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.50,0:11:40.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,弄得好紧张…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.67,0:11:43.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,即使回自己的房间里来也只能是干巴巴地坐着
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.96,0:11:48.01,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,截稿日之前  寻学姐也不轻松呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.74,0:11:51.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,或许我就做不到这样
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.86,0:12:01.52,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,（3月13日  全校放假的通知）
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.54,0:12:12.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.10,0:12:14.97,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an1}香草配方
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.10,0:12:14.97,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an9}咽喉清爽
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.70,0:12:16.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,Safe
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.72,0:12:22.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,干吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.59,0:12:30.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,喂～
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.41,0:12:32.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小宫
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.52,0:12:34.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,应该把膝盖盖上的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.28,0:12:36.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.48,0:12:37.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我也来待一会吧～
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.03,0:12:38.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,可以啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.01,0:12:40.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,本不必陪着我的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.36,0:12:42.46,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你也会冷着的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.10,0:12:44.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我也给自己准备了一条
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.46,0:12:48.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,觉得暖和些了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.55,0:12:51.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.22,0:12:53.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,校长
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.21,0:12:56.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,明明放假了居然还在学校
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.71,0:12:58.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是买饭回来了么？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.57,0:12:59.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,或许是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.72,0:13:00.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,咦？葱？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.08,0:13:03.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,原来校长是自己做饭啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.25,0:13:06.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,在学校做饭？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.65,0:13:07.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,他不是也教家政课的么？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.35,0:13:12.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是  为什么校长要做饭呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.34,0:13:14.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,而且是假期的学校里…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.96,0:13:17.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,莫非校长他…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.28,0:13:20.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,住在学校？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.02,0:13:24.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真不愧是校长呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.19,0:13:26.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,果然够校长的资格
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.13,0:13:30.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,校长真的是非常喜欢山吹呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.28,0:13:33.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小宫是来看数学的？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.89,0:13:34.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.67,0:13:35.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,由乃都在用功
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.11,0:13:36.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我也要加油
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.64,0:13:40.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,在自己房里学不会更好么？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.68,0:13:42.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,在房里就要睡着了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.18,0:13:43.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是么？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.01,0:13:44.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.99,0:13:47.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,「春眠不觉晓」
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.16,0:13:48.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,来吧来吧～
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.21,0:13:50.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,来吧来吧～
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.50,0:13:51.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,数～学～
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.80,0:13:52.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,来吧来吧～
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.17,0:13:54.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,觉得有点奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.12,0:13:56.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不要紧么？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.51,0:13:58.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,当然
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.00,0:14:11.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小宫你想喝茶么？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.70,0:14:12.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,要啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.88,0:14:14.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,还有些点心哟
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.50,0:14:17.87,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7}智花\N妈妈\N沙英学姐\N梅老师(原作者)\N寻学姐\N新房先生\N短信  工具
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.42,0:14:15.94,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.17,0:14:18.93,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊～
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.92,0:14:20.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哦～
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.53,0:14:24.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,昨天睡太多了  弄得头疼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.76,0:14:26.97,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,（>_<）现在在发呆中
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.14,0:14:28.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,什么也没干…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.40,0:14:31.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,想和由乃同学  宫子同学一起
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.53,0:14:33.19,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,去卡拉OK啊—
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.69,0:14:36.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,由乃同学最喜欢的歌手是谁呢～？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.41,0:14:38.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不错嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.61,0:14:40.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我也想去卡拉OK
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.52,0:14:40.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.28,0:14:42.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,一定去哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.12,0:14:46.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我最喜欢的歌手是「人鱼」
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.27,0:14:48.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这样行了吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.68,0:14:50.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,再加上「去读一下月刊亮晶晶」
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.08,0:14:51.56,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,（发送）
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.17,0:14:56.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  老师好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.62,0:14:57.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好～
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.82,0:14:58.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你们好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.71,0:15:00.09,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,由乃同学  宫子同学
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.87,0:15:03.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,吉野屋老师是假期来值班的么？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.09,0:15:04.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.98,0:15:06.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,今天是来玩的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.28,0:15:07.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.97,0:15:10.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,吉野屋老师也很喜欢山吹呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.17,0:15:12.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不是没法子么…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.60,0:15:14.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,爸妈对我说
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.47,0:15:18.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,「难得休假就别窝在家无所事事」
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.14,0:15:21.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我就是因为休假才窝在家的…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.09,0:15:23.94,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,被家里人赶出来了么？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.30,0:15:25.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不·是！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.94,0:15:28.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是我自己要出来的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.53,0:15:29.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.35,0:15:31.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你现在即使道歉我也不原谅你了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.03,0:15:35.22,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,虽说是休假
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.89,0:15:37.09,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不过机会难得
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.46,0:15:40.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就特别地给由乃同学开个小灶吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.77,0:15:41.27,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.92,0:15:48.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,诶…那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.56,0:15:51.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,请指定我要站的位置吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.57,0:15:53.93,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,pose就我来决定了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.74,0:15:55.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.60,0:15:57.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你肯在这里等我一下的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.48,0:15:59.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我回去拿衣服来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.68,0:16:03.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,吉野屋老师算是离家出走的吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.65,0:16:06.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,为了由乃同学的话我会偷偷跑回去拿的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.86,0:16:11.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我说那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.83,0:16:16.22,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,校长拿着什么啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.00,0:16:17.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,酱油
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.41,0:16:20.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才是忘记买了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.41,0:16:24.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就因为这样才没有放在塑料袋里啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.94,0:16:27.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,校长好强的环保意识
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.81,0:16:29.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不过我说
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.58,0:16:30.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,他什么时候出来的呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.30,0:16:32.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我觉得是利用warp
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.30,0:16:32.58,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,（注：SF作品中warp指利用宇宙空间的扭曲进行的瞬时移动…）
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.83,0:16:33.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.68,0:16:36.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,没想到校长居然在这里…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.03,0:16:39.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,倒不如说其实校长是住在学校里的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.91,0:16:41.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,诶～
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.82,0:16:48.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我说
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.81,0:16:50.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,像刚才那种时候
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.53,0:16:51.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,要怎么办才好啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.28,0:16:53.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你讨厌画她？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.67,0:16:56.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,也不是讨厌…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.09,0:16:59.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不如说刚才有点没那个心情…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.16,0:17:01.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那么装做要画的样子什么的？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.28,0:17:04.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这种把戏瞬间就会被识破的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.34,0:17:08.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  要是还有机会的话真想见识一下
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.97,0:17:11.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不过这样她肯接受么？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.12,0:17:17.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这种时候  大人的话会怎样应对呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.12,0:17:20.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,大人是什么呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.43,0:17:22.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是什么呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.91,0:17:28.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,一点一点地继续下去么？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.17,0:17:29.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,说的是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.23,0:17:37.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,寻学姐
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.80,0:17:40.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  欢迎回来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.95,0:17:42.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,沙英学姐怎么样了啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.66,0:17:43.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么样了呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.56,0:17:47.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀呀
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.74,0:17:49.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小宫
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.71,0:17:51.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,柜子上面有毯子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.19,0:17:53.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,能帮我拿一条来么？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.95,0:17:54.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.10,0:17:57.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小说的事情不要紧吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.72,0:17:58.16,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.76,0:18:02.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,她说只剩最后一幕场景了  所以稍微睡一下
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.69,0:18:08.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,头不疼么？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.26,0:18:14.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,寻学姐  给你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.26,0:18:14.47,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,（这个…逗猫用的…）
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.05,0:18:16.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.20,0:18:24.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好的  完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.62,0:18:26.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嘿咻
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.26,0:18:31.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,诶～
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.22,0:18:31.93,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我也要？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.28,0:18:33.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,由乃也跳下来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.91,0:18:35.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小宫  你没有事吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.11,0:18:36.97,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,毫发无损
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.62,0:18:38.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,一…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.35,0:18:39.17,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,一…二…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.47,0:18:40.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  不行不行不行
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.14,0:18:42.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好可怕好可怕啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.74,0:18:43.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,由乃  come on
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.61,0:18:48.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,救…救我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.52,0:18:50.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,离地面也就1.5米而已啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.93,0:18:51.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,没事没事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.51,0:18:52.15,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,不行不行
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.44,0:18:53.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,都…都说了不行…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.10,0:18:54.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.19,0:18:57.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,彻底走光了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.90,0:19:01.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不过我觉得沙英学姐没有看到
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.52,0:19:02.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,寻学姐也不在
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.47,0:19:06.02,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小宫赶快忘了这事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.94,0:19:07.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.04,0:19:09.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.43,0:19:11.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,干杯！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.15,0:19:13.09,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,都说了不用
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.20,0:19:13.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.15,0:19:17.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,有好事就应该庆祝一下嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.06,0:19:20.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好事是…好事…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.05,0:19:22.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,祝贺祝贺
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.76,0:19:23.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.49,0:19:27.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,今天写的什么时候能出版呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.33,0:19:29.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,大概下个月吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.67,0:19:32.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,出版了的话我们再去看吧  小宫
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.33,0:19:33.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就这么着
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.40,0:19:35.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,由乃你说「再」？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.63,0:19:38.63,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,今天我和小宫一起去过书店了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.11,0:19:42.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,呃…是关于一对姐妹的故事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.59,0:19:44.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.35,0:19:46.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我并没有告诉你们我的笔名的…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.56,0:19:47.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哈哈哈
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.70,0:19:49.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你以为瞒得住么？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.98,0:19:51.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这不是很好吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.37,0:19:57.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我倒是希望沙英的小说被更多的人了解
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.66,0:20:00.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这次的故事也非常有趣哟
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.18,0:20:01.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真的么？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.23,0:20:02.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.44,0:20:04.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这次的故事是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.85,0:20:08.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,健介和奈奈美是住在同一座公寓的青梅竹马
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.81,0:20:12.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,虽说从小时候开始关系就非常好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.59,0:20:16.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不过进入高中后才开始觉察到对方的异性魅力…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.82,0:20:18.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,寻你这家伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.97,0:20:19.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.33,0:20:22.63,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,出版了的话大家都能读到的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.03,0:20:24.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,虽说如此
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.28,0:20:25.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不喜欢还是不喜欢…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.36,0:20:28.94,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  最后那场告白
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.27,0:20:30.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,读得我也心儿怦怦地跳呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.08,0:20:32.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我说你别说了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.70,0:20:33.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.62,0:20:36.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那也是描写沙英学姐的亲身经历啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.69,0:20:38.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,当然啦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.17,0:20:42.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我的告白啊…像星星那么多…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.17,0:20:42.04,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,（注：她说的是“告白した”而不是“告白された” 是她对别人告白而不是别人对她…）
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.63,0:20:44.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那么就是说你还有库存了？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.82,0:20:46.63,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  得用亿来数
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.07,0:20:52.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  寻学姐她们太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.22,0:20:54.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,互相理解
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.70,0:20:55.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,互相信赖
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.09,0:21:00.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我和小宫也有一天能成为那样的吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.91,0:21:01.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯～
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.15,0:21:08.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我可是一直在募集给我做饭的人哟
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.12,0:21:11.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,呃…我倒不是这个意思…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.67,0:21:13.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小宫不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.59,0:21:16.46,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我忘记帮你收了一个包裹了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.92,0:21:18.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你来取一下吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.55,0:21:19.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.64,0:21:22.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,什么啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.57,0:21:23.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,沉甸甸的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.58,0:21:24.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,会是什么呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.75,0:21:26.82,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,（北海水产）
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.75,0:21:26.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,北海之惠
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.16,0:21:26.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不是真的吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.13,0:21:32.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,其实之前我参加了有奖问答活动
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.88,0:21:34.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,中奖了啊  小宫
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.80,0:21:36.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,太厉害了  祝贺你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.80,0:21:37.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.66,0:21:40.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.68,0:21:43.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,华丽的北海之惠啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.90,0:21:48.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不过
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.94,0:21:54.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我和小宫也差不多是寻学姐她们那种亲密关系了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.83,0:21:58.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,正因为有小宫陪着
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.74,0:22:01.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我才能完成那画的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.31,0:22:10.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,3月13日  完  待续
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.02,0:23:44.17,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊～
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.14,0:23:46.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,诶？由乃她…？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.74,0:23:48.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,只吃了一碟咖喱
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.64,0:23:51.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,早上也是推说没有时间只吃了一片面包
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.24,0:23:52.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,一般人都是如此吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.47,0:23:54.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,难道是恋爱的烦恼么？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.62,0:23:57.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  由乃同学变成大人了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.65,0:23:58.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,什…什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.70,0:24:01.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你说我做了什么啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.93,0:24:02.46,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,下次是
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.75,0:24:05.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,「9月4日  里新宿之狼」
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.68,0:24:07.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我们在山吹高中等着你
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.52,0:24:09.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,一定要来看哦
